Usage: set_instance_library [-help] -library <string> -instance <string> [ -early  | -late  ]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-early                 # Use this library binding for early timing analysis.
                       # (bool, optional)
-instance <string>     # The instance for which the library binding needs to be
                       # done. (string, required)
-late                  # Use this library binding for late timing analysis.
                       # (bool, optional)
-library <string>      # Library File Path (string, required)